snippet.title: No Time to Waste (SFM) - Pirates, Vikings & Knights II Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Pirates, Vikings & Knights II is a free game you can get on Steam: (http://store.steampowered.com/app/17570/)

Thanks to AGSMA - who is a part of the PVKII crew - for the awesome idea for the video, as well as his very fitting song suggestion.
Music: Gioacchino Rossini - La Gazza Ladra, from Opus 1 Music
(http://www.opus1.sourceaudio.com/#!explorer). With permission: (https://www.dropbox.com/s/l12xdrlpk4co8qi/Proof%20of%20Permission%5B2%5D.pdf?dl=0)
